OL,3,CPolice warn of health risks from
OL,4,Csuspected illegal butchery after sheep
OL,5,Ctheft
OL,7,FWest Mercia Police have issued a
OL,8,Fwarning to consumers about potential
OL,9,Fhealth risks after sheep, unfit for
OL,10,Fhuman consumption due to medication,
OL,11,Fwere stolen in Chaddesley Corbett and
OL,12,Fpossibly butchered illegally for sale.
OL,14,FThe public is urged to buy meat only
OL,15,Ffrom reputable sources and to report
OL,16,Fany suspicious sales, particularly in
OL,17,FWorcestershire.
