OL,3,CPolice warn of health risks from
OL,4,Csuspected illegal butchery after sheep
OL,5,Ctheft
OL,7,FThe warning comes after several sheep
OL,8,Fwere stolen over the Bank Holiday
OL,9,Fweekend, prompting a police
OL,10,Finvestigation into suspected illegal
OL,11,Fbutchery.
OL,13,FInvestigators believe that the stolen
OL,14,Fsheep may have been slaughtered for
OL,15,Fmeat, despite the fact that the
OL,16,Fanimals were undergoing treatment with
OL,17,Fmedication that makes them unsafe to
OL,18,Feat.
