OL,3,CPolice warn of health risks from
OL,4,Csuspected illegal butchery after sheep
OL,5,Ctheft
OL,7,FThe presence of such medication in the
OL,8,Fmeat poses a serious health threat if
OL,9,Fconsumed, leading to concerns that it
OL,10,Fcould enter the food supply.
OL,12,FPolice are appealing for the public to
OL,13,Fexercise caution and ensure they
OL,14,Fpurchase meat only from trusted and
OL,15,Fverified sources and to immediately
OL,16,Freport any individuals or businesses
OL,17,Fselling meat under suspicious
OL,18,Fcircumstances.
