OL,5,Ctheft
OL,7,FAs the investigation continues,
OL,8,Fauthorities are working to trace the
OL,9,Fsource of the stolen sheep.
OL,11,FThe public is encouraged to assist by
OL,12,Fproviding any information that could
OL,13,Fhelp locate the perpetrators or
OL,14,Fprevent the distribution of unsafe
OL,15,Fmeat.
OL,17,FA West Mercia Police spokesperson
OL,18,Fsaid: "We're urging people to report
OL,19,Fsuspicious sales of meat following the
OL,20,Ftheft of three sheep in Chaddesley
OL,21,FCorbett over the bank holiday weekend.
