OL,3,CPolice warn of health risks from
OL,4,Csuspected illegal butchery after sheep
OL,5,Ctheft
OL,7,F"It's feared that the sheep may have
OL,8,Fbeen stolen to be illegally butchered
OL,9,Ffor meat. The animals were on
OL,10,Fmedication which would make their meat
OL,11,Funfit for human consumption."
OL,13,FPCSO Kate Easthope said: "We're
OL,14,Fconcerned that if the meat from these
OL,15,Fsheep has entered the food chain it
OL,16,Fcould cause serious health issues for
OL,17,Fthose who consume it.
OL,19,F"As always, for your safety we would
OL,20,Fonly advise buying and consuming meat
OL,21,Ffrom reputable sources.
